Schiltach has to take 220 000 euros in his hand.
Deutsche Bahn plans to improve the Kinzigtal line next year.
In particular, safety at level crossings is to be increased - there are regular collisions of trains with other vehicles throughout Germany.
If the municipalities agree to the conversion measures, they have to contribute with one third to the costs, the rest are shared by the railway and the federal government.
Schiltach's master builder Roland Grießhaber explained the peculiarities of the Bahübergang "Am Hirschen" to the municipal council.
