When Snowden speaks in Germany, he needs an assurance that he is "safe" there, the MP said.
Snowden explains in his letter that he was exposed to a "serious and ongoing" persecution campaign that drove him out of his home country.
However, he was touched by the global response to 'my act of political expression'.
